*She kept firing at Bumblebee. She started to back up a few feet.  She 
turned and ran towards a tree.  She got behind it and stood up against it.  
She looked at her wounds.  They were extensive.  Her shoulder was sliced 
through.  One of her ribs was exposed.  She knew she needed help and it 
would have to be soon or she would ceace to function.  She punched in her 
comlink and called out.*

"Maximal in trouble, big trouble.  I need help."

*Her breathing became labored and she was starting to gasp for breath.*

"I say again, Maximal in trouble.  I could really use some help here."

*All she could do now was pray for a miracle.  Although she knew she had one 
already, she wasn't to proud to hope for another one.*
